      <title>Go语言基础之变量与常量</title>
      <link>https://www.niuwx.cn/posts/golang/go%E8%AF%AD%E8%A8%80%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E4%B9%8B%E5%8F%98%E9%87%8F%E4%B8%8E%E5%B8%B8%E9%87%8F/</link>
